		<div id="p34915" class="post" data-posted="1393918828" data-group-id="1">
			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p34915" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>119</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://novejshaaj.mybb.ru/viewtopic.php?id=1043&amp;p=4#p34915">2014-03-04 11:40:28</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
